<h1>Password Reset</h1>

<p>
  Hi <%= @user.name %>, \n
  Please click on link below to reset your password.
</p>

<p><%= link_to "Password Reset", edit_password_reset_url(@user.reset_token, email: @user.email) %></p>

<p>Note: the link will expire in two hours.</p>

<p>If you don't require your password to be reset, please ignore this email. You password will stay as it is.</p>